{"tid":2054014,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「證明」六四和平撤出天安門嘅片段","createTime":"2020-06-06T19:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T09:23:26.000Z","uid":311495,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5ef0bad80c4b070d0961b759a640a9a068047b","tid":2054014,"uid":311495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T19:38:35.000Z","msg":"呢幾日又有唔少五毛走出嚟<br />\n話有片段證明六四無傷亡<br />\n仲特登點名話係一間西班牙電視台拍到嘅<br />\n<br />\n網上唔難搵到其他電視台嘅片<br />\n但應該只有呢個電視臺RTVE影到四號凌晨四點左右嘅片段<br />\n所以亞視1994年先至會買嚟播<br />\n但亞視將佢剪過<br />\n只係提部分槍炮向人頭上射煙霧彈<br />\n扮到大致和平撤退咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cwi6PVlSWXI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dcwi6PVlSWXI&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUhmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=6c8af7a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cwi6PVlSWXI</a><br />\n<br />\n係好舊嘅片，但我搵唔到有人攞呢條片同亞視嘅比較<br />\n條片雖然影唔到實際清場屠殺片段<br />\n但係果陣大部分記者都唔敢留低<br />\n得好少人仲有紀錄緊<br />\n呢段片有一定歷史價值<br />\n亦都影到唔少死傷者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rtve.es/alacarta/videos/en-portada/portada-madrugada-sangrienta/5252894/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rtve.es%2Falacarta%2Fvideos%2Fen-portada%2Fportada-madrugada-sangrienta%2F5252894%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUhmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=338eb7aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rtve.es/alacarta/videos/en-portada/portada-madrugada-sangrienta/5252894/</a><br />\n<br />\n亞視將呢啲剪晒，好無恥咁扭曲歷史<br />\n依加仲俾人當埋係真相"},{"pid":"d663c83c300a25b1899eef739cbfd439eaf9f12b","tid":2054014,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T19:45:15.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"877460ec375a88d3390e7c81091c249a508410b4","tid":2054014,"uid":311495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T21:03:54.000Z","msg":"Timestamps<br />\n相同片段<br />\n亞視 1:49; RTVE 10:59<br />\n亞視 4:17; RTVE 14:18<br />\n<br />\nRTVE後半內容比較血腥<br />\n具體時間同埋一啲鏡頭冇直接影到嘅事件好重要，但我唔識聽西班牙文<br />\n<br />\n謝志峰喺當日(